<DOCID> 029832 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 7, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Westside; Part J; Page 16 
</P>
