DUCKS ADJUST TIME FOR GAME 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Mighty Ducks said the time of their April 13 game against Vancouver at The 
Pond of Anaheim has been changed to 8:05 p.m. The change was made to avoid 
schedule and traffic conflicts with the Angels-Cleveland Indians game, which 
