<P>
PREP ROUNDUP; HESS' TWO VICTORIES HELP CANYON BEAT ORANGE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Double-winner Lisa Hess took first in the 100 butterfly and the 200 freestyle 
to help Canyon beat Orange, 100-70, in a girls' Century League dual meet 
Wednesday at Orange High. 
</P>
<P>
 Hess' time in the butterfly, 1:00.40, was the fastest time recorded this 
season and her 1:59.9 in the 200 freestyle put her in this year's top five 
times in the county. 
</P>
<P>
 Canyon remains undefeated at 6-0, 2-0. 
</P>
