O'Kelley each won two events for Los Alamitos (5-0, 2-0). Paradeise won the 50 
freestyle (25.66) and the 100 butterfly (1:00.86), Schubert won the 100 (55.64) 
and 200 freestyle (2:02.32 and O'Kelley won the 200 medley (2:16.32) and the 
500 freestyle (5:25.58). 
