<TEXT>
<P>
 An independent consultant is investigating allegations of discrimination 
against women who work in the Pasadena city attorney's office. 
</P>
<P>
 The investigation into whether City Atty.Victor J. Kaleta discriminated 
against his female employees is to be completed in several weeks, said Ramon 
Curiel, director of affirmative action, who would not release details of the 
probe. 
</P>
