CITY HALL JOURNAL; NORWALK; CITY OKS $23-MILLION COMMERCIAL COMPLEX 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JILL GOTTESMAN 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The City Council has approved a $23-million retail and entertainment complex 
that will include 24 movie theaters, five restaurants and 10,000 square feet of 
retail space on a 10-acre site at Norwalk Boulevard and the Santa Ana (5) 
Freeway. 
</P>
<P>
