million people per year and will bolster the city's dwindling retail sales tax 
base. The city has agreed to a 99-year lease with Swanson's El Segundo-based 
Metropolitan Development Associates, which guarantees the city $450,000 a year, 
the developer said. 
</P>
<P>
 Swanson said the complex will be finished in three to four years. JILL 
