<P>
 DUARTE UNIFIED: The district received two awards from the California 
Department of Education for its Dropout Prevention Program, which has reduced 
Duarte's dropout rate from 58% to less than 5% during the past seven years. The 
awards were for Best Coordinated Districtwide Program in the State, and for 
Middle School of the Year, which went to Northview Intermediate School. 
</P>
