 DeVon Edwards of Cal Poly Pomona set a meet record at the Riverside 
Invitational with a time of 46.29 seconds in the 400-meter dash. 
</P>
<P>
 Edwards, a junior, eclipsed the mark of 46.65. He has already met the NCAA's 
qualifying automatic standard. 
</P>
