<P>
 Orange County Development Announced: Home builder Kathryn Thompson has teamed 
with Freeman, Spogli & Co., a major private investment banking firm, in a 
four-year, $300-million project to build 1,200 low-cost homes in Aliso Viejo, a 
planned community in south Orange County. The partnership has purchased 162 
