<P>
 Wilson effigy -- A story in Tuesday's editions misidentified the site of a 
protest in which conservative activists burned Gov. Pete Wilson in effigy. That 
event took place outside a California Republican Party convention in Anaheim, 
not at a meeting of the California Republican Assembly. 
